The hospital nominally sides with the BASTION - for they also seek to heal and preserve - but should an injured Pyre warrior find their way to the hospital and behave themselves, their wounds will be tended to as well. However, given equally grave injury or illness, the hospital will always tend to civilians first, warriors second, and those that disrupt the hospital's work third.

Lore / More Info: Who Wanders AKA Altiyah Mu'Talid Hunts for Bastion A Jackaracal bounty hunter wizard from a lost desert tradition. Short Bio: Constantly haunted by visions and apparitions of his mentors, students, and past, Altiyah Mu'Talid, who goes by the stage name of Who Wanders based on his name, seeks to gather up enough money and knowledge from across the world to rebuild the temple that he grew up in and reestablish his order, as he struggles with staying on the path of righteousness. (Quite the run on sentence, I know.) Fighting style and skills: He learned his magic and martial skills from The Mystery School of The High Desert's Defenders, where he picked up the morals and tenants that he attempts to follow today of Justice, Prudence, Fortitude, Courage, Purpose, Temperance, and Self-Confidence. These values are always challenged as he hunts and fights, attempting to stick to his path and keep his magic under control. His martial skills come from the schools of the River of Life and the Desert Wind which taught him to flow and defend as well as striking hard and fast with his spear, staff, and batons. Also an important note is that the ends of his batons and staff ignite into the spear in a Kars light blade way. Personality: Cold but definitely not uncaring, he constantly keeps his hand on his weapons in some way as he traverses the world of the bounty hunter. He comes off as a dick and for sure the ultimate straight-man, but it's not out of a place of malice as he's constantly on high alert, defending himself to ensure that his tradition and legacy carries on. He definitely has a warmer side though if said person proves themselves to not be a threat in some way. He's a cat thing though so keep that in mind when he hunts.
